              <td>Less than 5 GB/month</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td scope="row">You stream music, upload photos on social media and browse the internet</td>
              <td>5 - 10 GB/month</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td scope="row">You stream video and are always online</td>
              <td>10+ GB/month</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        
      </table>
      <p>If you already have a Verizon prepaid plan, see your <a href="https://m.vzw.com/hyFeIhA5"
          target="_blank">usage details</a> for actual numbers.
      </p>
      <p>
        You can <a href="https://m.vzw.com/8jWahOXM" target="_blank">change your plan</a> or <a
          href="https://www.verizon.com/digital/nsa/secure/ui/myusage/" target="_blank">add data</a> using My
        Verizon.
      </p>
      <p>
        Note: Data usage for mobile hotspot devices depends on how many devices are connected to it and what they're
        doing. Usage could be 30 GBs or more if 3 devices are streaming music or video.
      </p>
